hey nora!! just ran the inventory sync and found some SKUs that will block dispatch.

these enabled SKUs have NO cost data at all — no PO cost and no override. any order containing them will refuse to ship:
<ul>
<% @costless_skus.each do |sku| -%>
  <li><%= link_to sku.sku, sku.zenventory_url || "#" %></li>
<% end -%>
</ul>

you can fix this by adding a declared_unit_cost_override on the SKU.

ok that's all!!
